prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D watercolor illustration for a greeting card front. In the style of a humorous, lighthearted watercolor painting with soft flowing colors, visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds.

The scene features cartoon-style illustrations of the young East Asian woman and young Southeast Asian man from the reference photo, standing together in the same pose. They are rendered to highly resemble their real-life counterparts, including their exact hairstyles, smiling facial expressions, glasses on the woman, and body proportions. The woman is on the left, wearing a light blue sweatshirt (no logo) and black pants. The man is on the right, standing slightly behind her with one arm around her, wearing a tan hoodie (no logo) and dark maroon pants.

They are standing on a pier, in front of a simplified, dreamy watercolor background of a calm bay with soft, muted blues and greys, and a distant shoreline suggested with loose, artistic washes of color.

Centered above the couple, in a beautiful, readable, and elegant handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Thanks for everything, Lao Lao!"

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
